***Charlie and the chocolate factory***
One day a boy named Charlie was standing at the side of the road and saw a factory that was closed for years working again. 
The factory was about chocolates that was loved by many people, after he saw the factory working again he rushed to his home and told his parents and grandparents. 
His grandparent known as granpa joe told him that he worked there and was happy by listening the news that the factory was back in buisness.
